            "excerpt": "Have you wondered about how to get more YouTube views? Well, you are not alone. Countless marketers, small business owners, amateur vloggers, and others are con...",
            "category": "Keyword Research Tips",
            "tags": [],
            "author": "Unknown",
            "authorInitials": "U",
            "date": "Nov 09, 2025",
