            "excerpt": "There are many ways to sell products online, and one of the most popular and profitable methods is through Amazon FBA. Online shopping has become part of the av...",
            "category": "Amazon",
            "tags": [],
            "author": "Unknown",
            "authorInitials": "U",
            "date": "Nov 09, 2025",
